view

  • Packages that use view 
    Package Description
    businessLogic  
  • Classes in view used by businessLogic 
    Class and Description
    AddCustomerFrame
    Class creates a window for entering data for a new customer to be added to the database Window will appear in when in the 'Admin' menu, 'Add customer' button was pressed
    AddProductFrame
    Class creates a window for entering data for a new product to be added to the database Window will appear in when in the 'Admin' menu, 'Add product' button was pressed
    DeleteCustomerFrame
    Class creates a window for entering id of customer to be deleted from database Window will appear in when in the 'Admin' menu, 'Delete customer' button was pressed
    DeleteProductFrame
    Class creates a window for entering id of product to be deleted from database Window will appear in when in the 'Admin' menu, 'Delete product' button was pressed
    EditCustomersFrame
    Class creates an editable window with the list of customers in database Window will appear in when in the 'Admin' menu, 'Edit customer' button was pressed
    EditProductsFrame
    Class creates an editable window with the list of Products in database Window will appear in when in the 'Admin' menu, 'Edit Product' button was pressed
    ListCustomersFrame
    Class creates an non editable window with the list of customers in database Window will appear in when in the 'Admin' menu, 'List customers' button was pressed
    ListProductsFrame
    Class creates an editable window with the list of Products in database Window will appear in when in the 'Admin' menu, 'List products' button was pressed
